</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
USAir is introducing a new service called Business Select for business-class
travellers.
Changes to the cabin will enable the airline to maximise revenue by
converting economy-class seats into Business Select seats between flights if
necessary. The size of the premium-class cabin can be expanded from the
