</XX>
<IN>P2731 Book Publishing.
    P6732 Educational, Religious, etc.
    Trusts.
</IN>
<XX>
Types:-
</XX>
<TP>MGMT  Management &amp; Marketing.
    PEOP  People.
    NEWS  General News.
</TP>
