<HEADLINE>
FT  12 SEP 94 / Inquiry to be held after crowd violence at boxing match
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The British board of control is to hold an inquiry into Saturday night's
violence. Board secretary John Morris said boxers and members of the
audience were put in danger.
</TEXT>
<XX>
