</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Johannesburg saw further profit-taking in fairly quiet trade as the market
continued its correction from recent highs. Golds gave up 13 to 2,463,
industrials fell 22 to 6,617 and the overall index was 52 lower at 5,955. De
Beers fell 25 cents to R110.
