FT  09 SEP 94 / World Commodities Prices: Market report
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By REUTER
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
Coffee prices closed the day off their lows but still Dollars 8 a tonne
below the previous close with the November futures contract at the London
Commodity Exchange closing at Dollars 3,920 a tonne. It was a dull session
as the market awaited fresh news of the Brazilian auctions.
